text.tspan: This is a random photo gallery. The photos were taken is Boston, New York &
White Mountains. This photo collection includes small wildlife, flora, farm,
and landscapes. Sometimes we don’t have to go to the most exotic places to
take interesting photos. No matter where you go, just take a camera, and
zoom in & out the lens, many exciting moments are waiting for you to catch
and share.
Site Name:
Zoom In & Out
Developer:
Pei Ren
FINAL PROJECT
PROPOSAL/WIREFRAMES
PHOTO
Project Goals:
Design & FEWD:
Choose some of the photos taken in Boston, White Mountains &
New York and create a random photo gallery web site. This photo
collection shows small wildlife, flora, farm, and landscapes.
At the same time, delivered the following message to
photography enthusiast:
Sometimes we don’t have to go to the
most exotic places to take interesting
photos. No matter where you go, take a
camera, zoom in and out the lens,
many exciting moments are waiting for
us to catch and share.
Will have a clean design layout with easy navigation & buttons
(make nav and buttons fixed to allow users easily navigate to
whatever interests them next no matter where they are
looking). In addition, add interactivity and animations to
make the site fun and interesting.
